"但係冇不反對通知書下 大家會點樣表態？"},{"pid":"1b3576a26703af638047f6f38e3e2b3413b92ddb","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:03:02.000Z","msg":"原本係維園到總政"},{"pid":"c9ab5b2adda5a905d75c8abbf9886cb945d62742","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:03:51.000Z","msg":"大家比啲意見 差佬一早芒實連登"},{"pid":"fc99a31913ac8c103933207044cc5b166c4179a8","tid":1225002,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"出"},{"pid":"8b539c205b4d29f1e142021511fc361fc128950b","tid":1225002,"uid":13754,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"51eb20c17f4c608463036a3bcacb01e3617afa6e","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"50ade102eb97709d6d8bf89c8c03d3b6ec7572fc","tid":1225002,"uid":13754,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:02:10.000Z","msg":"616重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 撤回惡法<br />\n2. 撤回暴動指控<br />\n3. 撤銷對手無寸鐵、和平示威者之起訴<br />\n<br />\n另加一個<br />\n撤銷官員、警察及損害香港民主人權者進入外國旅遊、工作或居留的權利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:02:43.000Z","msg":"但係冇不反對通知書下 大家會點樣表態？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:04:28.000Z","msg":"你聽日去港島咪知啲人點表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n使乜喺度正負評？"},{"pid":"b934fcdf373c2f59980fb72af66e94c4c906be9f","tid":1225002,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fc99a31913ac8c103933207044cc5b166c4179a8","tid":1225002,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:04:55.000Z","msg":"去附近行街買野"},{"pid":"8a939fcae960546f5df2a1ec7b1755f174562df4","tid":1225002,"uid":18948,"like":275,"dislike":0,"score":275,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/archive/doc/201200c.doc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doj.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Farchive%2Fdoc%2F201200c.doc&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a34b00de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/archive/doc/201200c.doc</a><br />\n<br />\n3.​最普遍的誤解，是公眾遊行必須得到警方批准。我希望所有議員現在明白，事實並非如此。《公安條例》只是就大部分超過30人的公眾遊行，訂立了一項通知警方的規定。<br />\n<br />\n4.​警務處處長在接到舉行公眾遊行的意向通知後，除非反對舉行遊行，否則必須發出不反對通知書。如果處長在指定期限內沒有發出不反對通知書，也沒有發出反對遊行的通知，他便會被當作已發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n5.​換言之，如果警方不發出反對通知，遊行便可進行，顯而易見，法例並無規定遊行必須得到警方批准。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟要講幾多次"},{"pid":"20f1e3b61d284db78377a622675510226c4ce242","tid":1225002,"uid":233325,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:06:49.000Z","msg":"唔好諗人地出唔出，要諗點樣令多啲人出<br />\n<br />\n我地其實未贏過，佢地諗住拖，拖到我地有一啲人無咁留意就偷偷地過，所以要認清目標，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>撤修例</strong></span></span>！<br />\n唔好俾人模糊焦點，唔好俾人分化，團結係最大籌碼，香港人，記住<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤不散</span></span></strong>!<br />\n<br />\n人數係最大優勢，請專注係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宣傳616遊行</span></span>！叫多啲人出黎，等人地無藉口話少左人反修例。<br />\n<br />\n附送實用post<br />\n今日文宣好重要 各位手足同我全部落街宣傳 見街站幫街站 暫你老母 緩你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224975</a><br />\n<br />\n[民意戰] 如何反駁常見支持修例謬論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224371</a><br />\n<br />\n親 愛國愛港 保民生 抗修例 大聯盟的第二波圖要來了<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223671/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223671/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n新長輩圖！用割蓆狗咬狗長輩圖，營造建制抗林鄭大聯盟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223634</a><br />\n<br />\n[612經驗] 其實呢幾日有咩注意<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1221184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1221184</a><br />\n<br />\n振興香港消費！全城戶外運動裝備及須知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224572</a><br />\n<br />\n我係急症室醫生，麻煩大家睇一睇，保護自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1217490\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1217490</a><br />\n<br />\n【 突發】第二輪炮火！行動升級！除咗取消港共外國護照，我地正式開辟聯合國人道罪行戰線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217474/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217474/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【 突發】正式開火！第一批信已發出！我地香港人要幫政府官員、保皇黨取消外國護照！<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1204306/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1204306/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n發夢夢見６１７活動成功紀錄（一）：聖詩及野餐篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1221199/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1221199/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n發夢夢見６１７活動成功紀錄（二）：抗爭者篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1221214/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1221214/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n野餐物資／通訊檢討小組（重開）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[612經驗] 其實呢幾日有咩注意[url]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1221184/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1221184/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n各位行街食飯用air drop幫手宣傳616遊行！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1221256\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1221256</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家616著黑衫、戴頭盔口罩出嚟遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1220126/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1220126/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n《保民生 抗修例 大聯盟》專頁今晨遭到封鎖鑰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224333</a>"},{"pid":"ea72a484ada41ed4f38b9eef341fdf79cc99e8d2","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"8b539c205b4d29f1e142021511fc361fc128950b","tid":1225002,"uid":13754,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"51eb20c17f4c608463036a3bcacb01e3617afa6e","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":1,"dislike