b","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:11:10.000Z","msg":"我知道 但身邊好多人都擔心 先想收集風向"},{"pid":"63ba3e9789b4c059a4af29e7d0165e223b335480","tid":1225002,"uid":11914,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:13:04.000Z","msg":"on9 根本冇人care 有冇通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3caf3c1c32109aa5ffd170cbf2ce4e4b6b215b0","tid":1225002,"uid":7790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:14:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/為什麼用-妨擾罪-而不是-非法集結罪/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%94%A8-%E5%A6%A8%E6%93%BE%E7%BD%AA-%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E7%BD%AA%2F&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=3d7f9893\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%82%BA%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E7%94%A8-%E5%A6%A8%E6%93%BE%E7%BD%AA-%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF-%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E7%BD%AA%2F&h=abdc7ca2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/為什麼用-妨擾罪-而不是-非法集結罪/</a><br />\n<br />\n根本要修改法例，阻止港共政府打壓民主運動。<br />\n<br />\n基本法第二十七條 ：<br />\n香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係，《公安條例》第18條「非法集結」，原本係搞黎針對以前黑社會吹雞打架，而家比港共拎黎告集會示威人士。之後發覺呢條好難告得入，又轉用「公眾地方妨擾」<br />\n<br />\n港共政府無所不用其極"},{"pid":"88fadebbd9b1c4a1304b32f4e2aa1f0e9fb9710c","tid":1225002,"uid":91721,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8a939fcae960546f5df2a1ec7b1755f174562df4","tid":1225002,"uid":18948,"like":275,"dislike":0,"score":275,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/archive/doc/201200c.doc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doj.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Farchive%2Fdoc%2F201200c.doc&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a34b00de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/archive/doc/201200c.doc</a><br />\n<br />\n3.​最普遍的誤解，是公眾遊行必須得到警方批准。我希望所有議員現在明白，事實並非如此。《公安條例》只是就大部分超過30人的公眾遊行，訂立了一項通知警方的規定。<br />\n<br />\n4.​警務處處長在接到舉行公眾遊行的意向通知後，除非反對舉行遊行，否則必須發出不反對通知書。如果處長在指定期限內沒有發出不反對通知書，也沒有發出反對遊行的通知，他便會被當作已發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n5.​換言之，如果警方不發出反對通知，遊行便可進行，顯而易見，法例並無規定遊行必須得到警方批准。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟要講幾多次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:14:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">通知咗警柒就行得架啦</span>"},{"pid":"30b83170137f7fd49f0db008801aa85da696cacf","tid":1225002,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"人多就唔使驚架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec460ae523991b75c9b6b0de53691f97ad18906","tid":1225002,"uid":97887,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9xCi4m0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9xCi4m0.png&h=e8c972aa&s={SIZE}\" />又話已申請不反對通知書？"},{"pid":"346b7f4f419f7ce08fbb32230be28ae5e63afd95","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"63ba3e9789b4c059a4af29e7d0165e223b335480","tid":1225002,"uid":11914,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:13:04.000Z","msg":"on9 根本冇人care 有冇通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"事實好多中產好怕 但佢哋又想行"},{"pid":"209cf00565e9f57e2ae8558c0d89c16ae63e9545","tid":1225002,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"346b7f4f419f7ce08fbb32230be28ae5e63afd95","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"63ba3e9789b4c059a4af29e7d0165e223b335480","tid":1225002,"uid":11914,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:13:04.000Z","msg":"on9 根本冇人care 有冇通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"事實好多中產好怕 但佢哋又想行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:19:47.000Z","msg":"咁撚多人怕春？"},{"pid":"1f27ed87ea3c9735402256e8776660c9a472f7a4","tid":1225002,"uid":15394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20f1e3b61d284db78377a622675510226c4ce242","tid":1225002,"uid":233325,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:06:49.000Z","msg":"唔好諗人地出唔出，要諗點樣令多啲人出<br />\n<br />\n我地其實未贏過，佢地諗住拖，拖到我地有一啲人無咁留意就偷偷地過，所以要認清目標，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>撤修例</strong></span></span>！<br />\n唔好俾人模糊焦點，唔好俾人分化，團結係最大籌碼，香港人，記住<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤不散</span></span></strong>!<br />\n<br />\n人數係最大優勢，請專注係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宣傳616遊行</span></span>！叫多啲人出黎，等人地無藉口話少左人反修例。<br />\n<br />\n附送實用post<br />\n今日文宣好重要 各位手足同我全部落街宣傳 見街站幫街站 暫你老母 緩你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224975</a><br />\n<br />\n[民意戰] 如何反駁常見支持修例謬論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224371</a><br />\n<br />\n親 愛國愛港 保民生 抗修例 大聯盟的第二波圖要來了<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1223671/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1223671/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n新長輩圖！用割蓆狗咬狗長輩圖，營造建制抗林鄭大聯盟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1223634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1223634</a><br />\n<br />\n[612經驗] 其實呢幾日有咩注意<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1221184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1221184</a><br />\n<br />\n振興香港消費！全城戶外運動裝備及須知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224572</a><br />\n<br />\n我係急症室醫生，麻煩大家睇一睇，保護自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1217490\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1217490</a><br />\n<br />\n【 突發】第二輪炮火！行動升級！除咗取消港共外國護照，我地正式開辟聯合國人道罪行戰線！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217474/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217474/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【 突發】正式開火！第一批信已發出！我地香港人要幫政府官員、保皇黨取消外國護照！<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1204306/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1204306/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n發夢夢見６１７活動成功紀錄（一）：聖詩及野餐篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1221199/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1221199/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n發夢夢見６１７活動成功紀錄（二）：抗爭者篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1221214/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1221214/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n野餐物資／通訊檢討小組（重開）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1217849/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[612經驗] 其實呢幾日有咩注意[url]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1221184/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1221184/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n各位行街食飯用air drop幫手宣傳616遊行！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1221256\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1221256</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家616著黑衫、戴頭盔口罩出嚟遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1220126/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1220126/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n《保民生 抗修例 大聯盟》專頁今晨遭到封鎖鑰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1224333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1224333</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:19:57.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，你完全做左我想做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThx 巴打，辛苦哂，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb66d98f6c5604f071bb978b9755bf37bed104f1","tid":1225002,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:21:19.000Z","msg":"佢咪試下唔好撚比lo 屌<br />\n和平遊行都唔撚比 仲要星期日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11b8c29ff906cb5e870cc5b1e129725549c0478","tid":1225002,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"唔出就係鬼"},{"pid":"ee0798a8bbb46e25905555587d12ae6e70ef613f","tid":1225002,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:22:20.000Z","msg":"諗深一層，依家我去行街得唔得？我去果度一定等於我集結緊？"},{"pid":"b24fa689fa007a065d4b4e982a6f8ff275c7b5dc","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"我會出 但講唔服佢哋出"},{"pid":"9c9178515b529d2a3ba08f522c3d669e25a48a77","tid":1225002,"uid":31389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"基本法講明有遊行 示威 集會自由<br />\n行使自由點解要佢同意<br />\n咩不反對通知書根本on9"},{"pid":"0fc771c9c9efb4430d8b65f05546312929e20746","tid":1225002,"uid":224402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e44983f80b531101aac5901302fc3ee5044f335e","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:01:43.000Z","msg":"咁岩想買波鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"香港人都行慣老銅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818777320a138f2c34973438ac67c75cdcd526b1","tid":1225002,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0fc771c9c9efb4430d8b65f05546312929e20746","tid":1225002,"uid":224402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e44983f80b531101aac5901302fc3ee5044f335e","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":119,"dislike":1,"score":118,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:01:43.000Z","msg":"咁岩想買波鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"香港人都行慣老銅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:28:02.000Z","msg":"聽日灣仔有玩具節<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b891b7d07f01fa63fb3c4918db7e10d214d605a","tid":1225002,"uid":149161,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:29:21.000Z","msg":"有不反對通知書 問撚完未啊"},{"pid":"774227e57856b632e2cc349ff0756de070de922e","tid":1225002,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a939fcae960546f5df2a1ec7b1755f174562df4","tid":1225002,"uid":18948,"like":275,"dislike":0,"score":275,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/archive/doc/201200c.doc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doj.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Farchive%2Fdoc%2F201200c.doc&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdegMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=a34b00de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/archive/doc/201200c.doc</a><br />\n<br />\n3.​最普遍的誤解，是公眾遊行必須得到警方批准。我希望所有議員現在明白，事實並非如此。《公安條例》只是就大部分超過30人的公眾遊行，訂立了一項通知警方的規定。<br />\n<br />\n4.​警務處處長在接到舉行公眾遊行的意向通知後，除非反對舉行遊行，否則必須發出不反對通知書。如果處長在指定期限內沒有發出不反對通知書，也沒有發出反對遊行的通知，他便會被當作已發出不反對通知書。<br />\n<br />\n5.​換言之，如果警方不發出反對通知，遊行便可進行，顯而易見，法例並無規定遊行必須得到警方批准。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟要講幾多次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f775669855d3e41162ff6cb44461d0ee8c3604","tid":1225002,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"百幾萬人陪你行都驚...<br />\n行果幾步路都要諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係叫你衝<br />\n難聽講句大肚婆都有膽過你地...."},{"pid":"e6136af7f508bc956b67c2dc91637ea360519d2f","tid":1225002,"uid":45120,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:32:25.000Z","msg":"講好撚多次<br />\n小學常識都有教<br />\n不反對通知書出唔出都好<br />\n只要你有申請 佢都必需要俾你示威<br />\n不反對通知書係冇實際作用 只係形式上要"},{"pid":"84f53ae53019ca228d235da382068182b5305d99","tid":1225002,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"209cf00565e9f57e2ae8558c0d89c16ae63e9545","tid":1225002,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"346b7f4f419f7ce08fbb32230be28ae5e63afd95","tid":1225002,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"63ba3e9789b4c059a4af29e7d0165e223b335480","tid":1225002,"uid":11914,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"cite